1.0.0.name: skeeks/yii2-widget-simpleajaxuploader
1.0.0.description: Javascript plugin for cross-browser Ajax file uploading with progress bar support. Works in all major browsers, including IE7+, Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Opera. No dependencies - use it with or without jQuery.
